Date of Last Revision: February 14th 2014

This app and any accompanying online or electronic documentation (the “App”) have been produced by and are the property of KnC Group AB (“KnC”). KnC is referred to as “us”, “we”, and “our” in this Privacy Policy. We are a company registered in Sweden, with company number 556948-9932. Our registered office is at Birger Jarlsgatan, 33 5tr, 111 45, Stockholm, Sweden. You can contact us by post to our registered office address or by email to info@kncwallet.com.

Please read the following carefully to understand KnC’s views and practices regarding your personal data and how we will treat it. KnC is committed to protecting your privacy.

This cookies, privacy and data policy (the “Privacy Policy”) tells you about how we collect, manage, use and store information about you which you provide in connection with the App. Please note that this Privacy Policy should be read in connection with the cookies and privacy policy of any applicable third party service provider (“App Store”), such as Google.

The App enables users to operate their own bitcoin wallet, by storing bitcoin directly onto the phone running the App. Bitcoin can be sent between the App wallet and the wallets of other App users or to any other bitcoin address.

In summary, we require permission to access the following data for the following reasons –

    Your phone number, which will be paired the information necessary to enable people to send bitcoin to you, and the phone numbers in your phone’s address book. We store this information remotely, but we do not remotely store information to enable us to know which phone number belongs to which particular individual. We use this information to find out which phone numbers in your address book are paired with other downloads of the App. This means you can find friends who also use the App.
    The other information in your phone's address book, such as the names and photos attributed to the phone numbers. We access this information on your phone but we do not store it remotely. If we find that one of your friends has also downloaded the App, we access and present this information to you when you communicate or transact with that person using the App.
    We may also use information in your social media accounts in a comparable way.
    If you provide contact details to us through the App, we may use that information to contact you about your use of the App or to notify you about our products and services.

